ecting constraints and modifications**\\n\\nI see that I need to inspect the constraints and check the style for a public class. The existing Commons_compilerTest has a package-private element that violates the requirement for all top-level classes to be public. I’m thinking I shouldn’t modify that directly. I also need to consider adding an import for 'File' and reading the ICompilerFactory interface. It's all about ensuring everything aligns with the current standards without making unnecessary changes!\", \"thinkingSignature\": \"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"rs_00cbef746c3021890169f93d6de494819483a114f7bd03b8c0\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"reasoning\\\",\\\"encrypted_content\\\":\\\"gAAAAABp-T1-llzGd9g8zycW6bRh1V9AlKnzgHzlJ3-mGaWsm81cQfSHEpjUYkagttFz5PN8Mx3nIEWQulOmft2zhp9pmY2oU53zY9VVlZIBxzRIfq6hXI8XTk6b5ddF89oCPEn4syBfQ1NSEYRGzHERcp8TaW82Njsqqb_rt2aKCfV8Wnys-ZQgt88QeXAm1hb9gIn19WJshlnRxtPRggm4g4XaLr9DkUPr8YlaPoXqJeF3iXf_qmmbVXS7MToVU8u2Non0y8l9NoXTHeLNH8m-Vl7opNKagf4E_fSJYxZoVH9inZYsZGKdSKggsKJjS5ItOUMmA5Vw7_8o9Y6cIF6ZIOC7Vn7msEY8HhcKBNkI4jVVdza6UkvHC4yt9nP13As45yzj1nwx4WxExVErFkqktRiZ0kbw0Z3wp9RTDJH6sbJ4StOpj4M8O9a2BcqdYtI2LQx0PQU3DTdi1g-3GdNZZr5mg1E0URQ9ZKiQlYjKdrl67TmafXwZnisjPBKi2dIS39H4lqoIdo2EuY-kZtFhiyvYZssZ52ufD7oZcCponaJ5Lr70_Lx9HBXePDgJlWcVsp8Wsgi70YWPDq1z_2AdwciFxRiDgQ4ccpH_8FG1ke2TRoVksHdGGTFxt4FR5OVVs3AMNfvkX4ITm8J-mykahXlJyAohbg40TW6KyprAdmxtA77fvbbTX1JnFiqKkUVdjTS90H8waL35BVIzAkBgqZi1FTvzHefh84Hltb7e_xQRNSqCiD_DLp2nkqipaHf-8BK6CQ2ojXp35GrSAeKw7GEUWIIatax-NJzoPK6lJBA4q9J0eGiU-07rH_k9yaTv-Ek6Dm_lnRVdp4NvA0sKpEavKYbXcp2OPND09KGKBnmrEM_0D7AKoui04MvuvTBxdPQ3mZHrfOh6KeqCOE8aMAMmBBkb_oYZUitTIJ5G1QtvFxVDTUNCugiBwIE32Tp4ZC3rW1-FhAIoc7Wjr3nrbW55FLeA_nTaLCG_kQBQq5utd54AU7FzMgaLxXa8lv9tAtcdqdQaEn1gU93Z-llWnjI9_PDbn6YfthoI9cCbM3MZS6j2i3yjWlPt5Tk6FFpvck-L5wI1z-3WHbxg6EK6fnW-W9TVaIncgOC0PVL3WPuWduv__mINPzxY5HV1KAt9qIxtB4Hg79jZpfo6KYagbNLuUfyXuDlIyPunneUn7dds0QVIH4XX1PUZF3Ek1XGoO1PLnQmaU6ehtTSN51kKVSYBLnYvtpMiJjAplp-WbNolPCOMhOCeKrzIDS7uSzNLQbegKqi8eKnsdsAzIilwGbxWkwA48cAlOFMTLpsVSF