t for 'File' and reading the ICompilerFactory interface. It's all about ensuring everything aligns with the current standards without making unnecessary changes!\\\"}]}\"}, {\"type\": \"toolCall\", \"id\": \"call_2M2Bu47XvDvj26dGp9Hw10X1|fc_00cbef746c3021890169f93d7ed54481949fe1473229c10f37\", \"name\": \"read\", \"arguments\": {\"path\": \"/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge9/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/source_context/org.codehaus.janino/commons-compiler/3.0.16/main/extracted/org/codehaus/commons/compiler/ICompilerFactory.java\"}}], \"api\": \"openai-responses\", \"provider\": \"OCA\", \"model\": \"gpt-5.5\", \"usage\": {\"input\": 1615, \"output\": 1047, \"cacheRead\": 13312, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"totalTokens\": 15974, \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"total\": 0}}, \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\", \"timestamp\": 1777941868970, \"responseId\": \"resp_00cbef746c3021890169f93d6d51dc8194b6862744338dbdce\"}, \"toolResults\": [{\"role\": \"toolResult\", \"toolCallId\": \"call_2M2Bu47XvDvj26dGp9Hw10X1|fc_00cbef746c3021890169f93d7ed54481949fe1473229c10f37\", \"toolName\": \"read\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"\\r\\n/*\\r\\n * Janino - An embedded Java[TM] compiler\\r\\n *\\r\\n * Copyright (c) 2001-2010 Arno Unkrig. All rights reserved.\\r\\n * Copyright (c) 2015-2016 TIBCO Software Inc. All rights reserved.\\r\\n *\\r\\n * Redistribution and use in source and binary forms, with or without modification, are permitted provided that the\\r\\n * following conditions are met:\\r\\n *\\r\\n *    1. Redistributions of source code must retain the above copyright notice, this list of conditions and the\\r\\n *       following disclaimer.\\r\\n *    2. Redistributions in binary form must reproduce the above copyright notice, this list of conditions and the\\r\\n *       following disclaimer in the documentation and/or other materials provided with the distribution.\\r\\n *    3. Neither the name of the